Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:44.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:51.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:59.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:07.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:16.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:24.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:32.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:40.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:48.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:56.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:44.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:51.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤独中寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:59.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用灵魂连结我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:07.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用爱恋温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:16.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那颤抖的祈愿之声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:24.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:32.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不断交替的轮回之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:40.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不终结的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:48.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不断轮回的 那些传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:56.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守护着安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努旺基
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 你也一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 我今天不是来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天有贼人入侵府邸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是这个村子的人把他藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁胆敢包庇他 我可绝不轻饶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们一大群人蜂涌而至
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图斯克尔 好久不见了喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这个样子 我现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间和你们纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得曾养育过一个这样说话的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图斯克尔 我也曾受过你不少照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:01:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 治疗痔疮的药见效了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道你们这些穷人的日子难过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很多方面都对你们睁只眼闭只眼了喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们也太得寸进尺了喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个老太婆给我抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:02:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对上了年纪的人来说地牢恐怕太冰冷了喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们居然做出这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个家伙？刚才扔石头的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆库鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢小看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自作主张…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵咪 我什么都不知道喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 药马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这里就交给艾露露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 一旦发生什么情况 请立即…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 请把这个喝下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚自己已经快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个过来让我再好好看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都是我引以为豪的孙女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小伤很快就会好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾露露越来越像我姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽且温柔的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露这个名字是我最喜欢的姐姐的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶您常说的那个故事是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的名字是由姐姐传承而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 你和我小的时候很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许现在很难想像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候大家都很疼爱我 直夸我可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 你们两人要好好地相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时有些争执也好 吵架也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们是这个世界上无可取代的两姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要两个人齐心协力 永远好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:07:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后 最后能请你答应我这老骨头一个请求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经活了足够长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对接下来的旅程也无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我担心的还是这两个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 请你留在这两个孩子的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶不一起的话我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两个可爱的孙女儿为我送终
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算是不枉此生了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已无任何遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无任何… 无任…何…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 奶奶 奶奶 奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图斯克尔她走了 就在刚才起程了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么没有保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 畜牲 畜牲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该考虑今后的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图斯克尔大人对我们来说有如亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有仁慈到看着亲人被杀还能继续沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你这么做图斯克尔她就会高兴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定不会原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 我也不能饶恕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这是由我造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和柚叶就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的厉害之处是让柚叶露出了笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那样的你 我也曾厌恶得恨不得杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 虽然不想承认 但是我也被你吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事情我只有你可以托付
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样都要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我要做的了断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贼 有贼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…好强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这里的士兵连我一个人都阻止不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准他 瞄准他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋就是努旺基么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不配知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻进来的老鼠就是这家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 形势逆转了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨桑迪 这下省得我去找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又年轻又精壮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今晚不会觉得无聊了喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为凭你这乳臭未干的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就战胜得了这个国家里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最聪明最优雅最尊贵最高强的武士吗喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个只懂得摆臭架子的肉球罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是只嘴硬的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图斯克尔她把一切都托付给小哥你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从今以后 小哥你就是村长了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 告诉我们现在应该怎么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会跟着小哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我根本当不了村长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其他人都不行 只有小哥才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们原本是因为战争和权力斗争而失去故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是因为不白之冤被追捕而逃到了边境的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到了这种边境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要死在路边的时候是图斯克尔大人救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请您务必 务必助少主一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道自己将要做的是什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是一条不归之路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 你这大将冲锋在前可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经没法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 第一场仗就应由我冲在最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然那么不珍惜这好不容易才拾回来的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是你的同伴们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在似乎还挺顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是军队数量上相差悬殊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会被镇压下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你能够活下来 也会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既无大义也无名分 你们为什么要反抗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是为了生存吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话为何不在法制下安分的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就能填饱肚子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会饥寒交迫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以慰藉死去的亲友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像野兽的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将 你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找得我好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克罗 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上回到圣上那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管这里了吗 大将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 都已经冲到这里了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 你退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在指挥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小伤和图斯克尔大人所受的屈辱比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 您没事实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那个少主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多利 古拉 柚叶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 她正在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 大伙 还有哈克奥罗一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨桑迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愚蠢到还弄不清现在的状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这个莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干了绝不能干的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那个老太婆死掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别蒙我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那一个老太婆居然做出了这种事喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努旺基 努旺基 努旺基
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我什么事情也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷…子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去援助这样子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 大将说一的话我就不说二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有打算这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙出现后 所有都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙 是那家伙的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做是正确的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又欠了你一个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么 为什么你要来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道你们在干什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤已经不要紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点伤没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就无需客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我们知不知道自己在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事发至此 朝廷随时会派讨伐军过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路只有两条
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起战斗或者等着被全歼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你知道 那为什么还…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人死了 不就完事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这些话是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最 最无法原谅的就是利用了这一切的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我稍微这样休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:14.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}静かに訪れる　色なき世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:14.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}悄悄来访的 无色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:26.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}全ての時を止め　眠りにつく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:26.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}停止万物的时间 进入安眠


